\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Can you tell me the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Number four Devine Street Brew - it's Devine Street it was called. In the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 
Adelphi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 How long did you live there, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Yes, I was about - I'd be about - five when we left there and we went to George Street across Chapel Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 How long did you live there, a long time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Oh yes. Was quite big 'cos I can remember going with them, going to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 
Amley's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217  bakery when it was only a shop then of a Saturday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 This'd be the place you lived the longest wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Oh no. 45 Cannon Street was the longest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 As a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 child}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Oh yes, as a child, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Do you know why they moved from Devine Street to George Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well a bigger house it was. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Do you know where your father came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Yes. Cavan - County Cavan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 In Ireland?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 He came over at sixteen didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
Sixteen year old and he came as apprentice to a Mr O'Brien the plasterer that must have come I suppose originally from - from Ireland and he was sent over as his apprentice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did he always have this job on did he have any other types of jobs?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
No, I can't remember him any time only plastering and - slob making, you know, when they start making them ceiling slobs and things like that, it all come under the plastering.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 Didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217  you tell me he became his own boss eventually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well - bit of a boss like kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 He didn't do any part time jobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well she never went to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Do you know where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 From - she was born in the Adelphi.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 And she never went to work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 No, not as I remember 'cos she was always having children you know every - I never remember her working but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Do you ever remember your father being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well rained off and snowed off and - you know, where there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 was}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217  no - there was no dole and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 nothing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
 like that, you had to go on the sick or something in them says as you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Your mother had no jobs before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7809043 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Yes, she - oh she worked in the flax mill all her life up to getting }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7809043 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
 of course because - she used to say, you don't you're born when we come out of work and met with a pile of papers to stand at the top of Silk Street to sell papers when she'd done work. You know, they were so poor. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 What did she do in the flax mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Whatever - I don't know what they done, you know, I never worked in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 She wasn't a weaver of anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Something like - after that kind, I know they all went in the mill in them days in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 Adelphi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 And she never worked after she'd children? How many rooms were there at George Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Three bedrooms. Yes. And a cellar room, I remember there was always such a good big cellar, you know, that you could wash and do and, in
 fact, they used to let the cellars off, people for about two bob a week for poor people that had nothing in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did you ever do this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 No, but me mother took lodgers in there. She took men lodgers in there to help to - yes, suppose so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 How many rooms were there downstairs then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well there'd be three, there was a - a back }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 kitchen}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217  like and then the kitchen as we called it and a parlour and lobbied off. Lobbied off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did she have any paid help in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Was the washing done at home or sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Done at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did your mother make or mend the family clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Oh yes, she was always - doing. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15279682\charrsid7603217 
Well in fact you - everybody was so poor then I can remember us all of a Fri - every Friday night I can reme
mber up George Street this great big bath was there, one after the other one went in, then she always had a jug of - jug of senna pods and a little special cup and the one that drank it up quick - drank the tea up quick - the senna tea - they got two coff
e
es, but if you took your time you only got one, every Friday night, and then I've seen, we've used - I've seen her with - we've had no changes you see for - next day when - yes, no - but she's - I've seen her doing all the washing then in the bath water k
i
nd of thing starting it like that and putting all, they used to - the men used to wear all striped shirts like linen, you know, calico shirt, no sleeves in or out like that and been put - we used to have to put them on as nightdress, sit there while next 
morning, go to bed like that Friday night but was all clean for Saturday morning. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
