\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 No. My mother, - no, only children like going to concerts when the kids was on and what have you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 When your father got home in the evenings, how many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well he'd spend nearly every evening at home but he wouldn't come home from work 'til about eight o'clock, it was nearly time for bed.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 What time did he start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well he used 
to go in the pub, he used to go in and never come home from work half the time you see, unless it was Lent. When Lent started he went off the beer. He wouldn't have no drink, as true as God, and - my husband used to say, your old fellow's gone - hey, Lent
's on, your old fellow's gone off the beer, he's gone on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14765897\charrsid7603217 Guinness}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 . Used to kid like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did your mother ever go to the pub with your dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Not - do you know, I can never hardly remember her going much, unless there was a wedding or a party on or
 something in the lot of years. No, she wasn't - me mother wasn't one to go in the pub but she'd have a drink in the house as I say. Yes, and then - then she'd go and then as - as the time went on he used to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14765897\charrsid7603217 fetch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217  the bottle of beer you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did your dad belong to any clubs?
