\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Oh yes, I thought well she'll have a pensi
on and I'll be able to - our Mag said, I'll give her half a crown, I'll give her half a crown. Well half a crown was a lot before the war, even before this war that's just gone, you could do a lot with that. And we'd - and then she'd two or three at home 
- two at home not working - working, not }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7809043 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
 so she'd be on her feet. But she only got ten shilling pension you see but then she only lived fourteen month over - after that.
