r 'cos she was always ailing as I say, chest, and - I got her the house next door to me when I come up this end so I could be near her and I used to go down for their wash - oh no, he'd fetch it up her husband and then I'd go down with it on a Thursday, d
one for her you know, 'cos she was bad.
