\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Oh - well I suppose they'd mix with one another, I don't remember, I know when you went up from St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
