n up the brew, you was old enough then to go up there and she used to get - it was a Miss Maguire in standard four, she always taught standard four and she used to get hold of you and knock your head, you bright gem, she'd say, from St }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14765897\charrsid7603217 Anne\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 . Every lot she got, every year the lot, you bright gems, she always called us that. You bright gems from St - from St }{\rtlch\fcs1 
