 and that and - she always wore a big high thing, you know, net - net with a high thing on and, you know, them specs that go on the end of the us
e, used to take her off behind her back but - suppose she had to do it like, it was a fresh lot of children and when she'd be walking on a Whit Friday for years and years after she used to say, how are you Mary? I'd say good morning Miss Maguire. We used 
to say all sort be on the fire and all like that to her you know behind her back. She knew it like but there was -
