\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Who do you think she mixed with though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Well - the other teachers, they never seemed to bother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Who do you think the bosses would mix with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
Yes, well they went with - the - the - the foreman and the - the upper class, they didn't bother about the - the - the poor - the workmen. You'd see the - the manager of this and the manager of that, I think it goes on all over 'cos I'
ve worked twenty-four years now at Blakes Motors and then - but if there was anything going on then they'd only - the managing director'd only be with the managers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 What type of people went to church and what type went to chapel, did you notice a difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
Oh yes - the - well, you know, the - nearly all the Catholics had to go to church, we was always made that church first and there was no night mass in them days like you can go at half past six at night now if you miss and - but - there was v
ery good people, in fact one lives over there that used to go to the Mount Street Methodist, he still goes to Wheest Cornice something big now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Did you notice any big difference between the people who went to your church and the people who went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5270951 MB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 
Well - well they always seemed to be better off, the - the non-Catholics than - than us. Some road, yes, to me they always seemed to be - 'course we had to give what we had, what little bit you give to the church we did, you had to keep the prie
st in them days you know and that. Oh yes, everything had to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15294545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14364513\charrsid7603217 Were you aware of this?
